---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const pdgaMembershipUrl = 'https://www.pdga.com/membership';
const pdgaRulesUrl = 'https://www.pdga.com/rules/official-rules-disc-golf';
const pdgaRulesSchoolUrl = 'https://www.pdga.com/rules/schools';
const udiscUrl = 'https://udisc.com';
const pdgaDiscountCode = '268_EAFF';
---

<Layout
	title="2026 Membership Information"
	description="Learn what is included with your 2026 Avalon Disc Golfers membership, including AGM participation, PDGA affiliate discount details, bag tags, and member guidelines."
>
	<div class="relative text-center mb-12 py-14 bg-gradient-to-b from-primary-100 to-bg-primary rounded-lg overflow-hidden">
		<div class="absolute top-0 right-0 transform translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-10">
			<svg class="w-80 h-80" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor">
				<path d="M12 2C6.48 2 2 6.48 2 12s4.48 10 10 10 10-4.48 10-10S17.52 2 12 2zm0 18c-4.42 0-8-3.58-8-8s3.58-8 8-8 8 3.58 8 8-3.58 8-8 8z"/>
				<circle cx="12" cy="12" r="3"/>
			</svg>
		</div>
		<h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">2026 Membership Information</h1>
		<p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-primary-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 mb-0">
			We are very happy to have you as a member of Avalon Disc Golfers for the 2026 season.
			This page outlines your membership benefits and key information for disc golf in our province.
		</p>
	</div>

	<section class="mb-12 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-primary-100">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-6">Membership Benefits</h2>
		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
			<article class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 rounded-lg p-6">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-700 mb-3">Annual General Meeting</h3>
				<p class="text-primary-700 mb-0">
					With your membership you can attend, vote, and run for positions within ADG at our annual AGM.
					It is usually held late in the year, and members are contacted about four weeks in advance.
					All interested members are welcome.
				</p>
			</article>

			<article class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 rounded-lg p-6">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-700 mb-3">Professional Disc Golf Association</h3>
				<p class="text-primary-700 mb-4">
					DGNL is recognized as an affiliate club with the PDGA. As an ADG member, you can use DGNL affiliate
					code <code class="font-semibold text-primary-800">{pdgaDiscountCode}</code> at checkout for
					<code class="font-semibold text-primary-800">$5 USD off</code> your PDGA membership.
				</p>
				<a
					href={pdgaMembershipUrl}
					target="_blank"
					rel="noopener noreferrer"
					class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white py-2 px-5 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors"
				>
					PDGA Membership
					<svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
						<path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 17 17 7M9 7h8v8"/>
					</svg>
				</a>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="mb-12 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-primary-100">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Bag Tags</h2>
		<p class="text-primary-700 mb-6">
			As part of your membership, you will receive a custom wooden ADG bag tag and a custom wooden DGNL bag tag.
			They are a great way to show your membership and add a fun layer of competition throughout the season.
		</p>

		<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
			<article class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 rounded-lg p-6">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-700 mb-3">How ADG tags work</h3>
				<p class="text-primary-700 mb-0">
					Tournament and league play requires tags to be turned in at the start of the event. Tags are redistributed
					after the round in stroke-play order, regardless of division, with the lowest score receiving the lowest tag.
					Top five tags must be defended within a reasonable timeframe or returned to the pool. Casual rounds can still
					be played for tags, but tournament and league results are awarded by leaderboard standings.
				</p>
			</article>

			<article class="bg-primary-50 border border-primary-100 rounded-lg p-6">
				<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-primary-700 mb-3">How DGNL tags work</h3>
				<p class="text-primary-700 mb-0">
					Each DGNL tag is numbered and issued at random. If two DGNL members agree to a tag round, the lower score at
					the end of the round takes the lowest tag. League and tournament rounds are automatically considered tag rounds.
				</p>
			</article>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="mb-12 bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-primary-100">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-6">General Information</h2>
		<ul class="space-y-5 text-primary-700">
			<li>
				Members are expected to know and follow the PDGA Official Rules of Disc Golf.
				Need to brush up? Visit the
				<a href={pdgaRulesUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PDGA Official Rules</a>
				and
				<a href={pdgaRulesSchoolUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">PDGA Rules School</a>.
			</li>
			<li>
				Many members use
				<a href={udiscUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">UDisc</a>
				to track rounds, locate courses, and find leagues and tournaments.
			</li>
			<li>
				The Avalon region continues to grow, with two courses currently in St. John's:
				<ul class="mt-2 list-disc list-inside text-primary-700">
					<li>Confederation Hill DGC</li>
					<li>McNiven DiscGolfPark</li>
				</ul>
			</li>
		</ul>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-white p-8 rounded-lg shadow-md border border-primary-100">
		<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary-700 mb-4">Thank You</h2>
		<p class="text-primary-700 mb-4">
			Thank you again for supporting ADG and becoming a member of our growing community.
			Please feel free to reach out by email, through our website, or on any of our socials.
		</p>
		<p class="text-primary-700 mb-3">Looking forward to seeing you on the courses,</p>
		<p class="text-primary-800 font-semibold mb-1">Ed Hartling</p>
		<p class="text-primary-700 mb-5">President - Avalon Disc Golfers</p>
		<a
			href="mailto:avalondiscgolfers@gmail.com"
			class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-600 text-white py-2 px-5 rounded-md hover:bg-primary-700 transition-colors"
		>
			Email ADG
			<svg class="w-4 h-4" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" aria-hidden="true">
				<path d="M20 4H4c-1.1 0-2 .9-2 2v12c0 1.1.9 2 2 2h16c1.1 0 2-.9 2-2V6c0-1.1-.9-2-2-2zm0 4l-8 5-8-5V6l8 5 8-5v2z"/>
			</svg>
		</a>
	</section>
</Layout>
